text.div:
DeviceDefinitionPropertyCode

Codes for identifying device properties. This is based upon IEEE/HCD specified codes.

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include these codes as defined in urn:iso:std:iso:11073:10101
    CodeDisplayDefinition
    68219MDC_TIME_CAP_STATETime capability
    68220MDC_TIME_SYNC_PROTOCOLTime synchronization method
    68221MDC_TIME_SYNC_ACCURACYThe accuracy of the time synchronization
    68222MDC_TIME_RES_ABSThe resolution of the absolute time clock
    68223MDC_TIME_RES_RELThe resolution of the relative time clock
    68224MDC_TIME_RES_REL_HI_RESThe resolution of the high resolution time clock
    68226MDC_TIME_RES_BOThe resolution of the base offset time clock
    532353MDC_REG_CERT_DATA_CONTINUA_CERT_DEV_LISTThe specializations this device is certified for
    532354MDC_REG_CERT_DATA_CONTINUA_REG_STATUSThe regulation type and status this device has
    532355MDC_REG_CERT_DATA_CONTINUA_PHG_CERT_LISTThe upload transactions this gateway has been certified for
